    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201430/extras/9f211a6c0c17a83164b5ca1be95d548e.avif?t=1726635915\" width=638 height=91 /></span><br>Join <strong>Tara Estelar</strong> on her debut adventure into the outskirts of the mysterious town of <strong>Stayfer River</strong>. Unwittingly embark on this mystery tour of an eccentric's farm to help solve the case of seemingly systematic sabotage that just might be steeped in the supernatural.<br><br>Use Tara's camera to view and photograph strange creatures named <strong><i>Geists</i></strong>. They don't always appreciate your presence though, so prepare for a fight!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201430/extras/4a42579751662e645ef95554fb8a05ba.avif?t=1726635915\" width=800 height=450 /></span><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201430/extras/7efdf9aed714ceb7ea2676146dbf209d.avif?t=1726635915\" width=638 height=91 /></span><br><br>Tara may choose to fight and <strong>Banish</strong> these terrifying anomalies or see the good in them and <strong>Appease</strong> them! You may find some things feel different depending on the paths you take...so choose wisely.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201430/extras/c77a94bd654058bb2ad15cb380bcc4b8.poster.avif?t=1726635915\" width=360 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201430/extras/c77a94bd654058bb2ad15cb380bcc4b8.webm?t=1726635915\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201430/extras/c77a94bd654058bb2ad15cb380bcc4b8.mp4?t=1726635915\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201430/extras/2edb2c701cb8ebfc6ca66e57c0ae073b.avif?t=1726635915\" width=638 height=91 /></span><br><br>Capture and build your album of Geist photographs to delve deeper into the story behind their sudden appearance!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201430/extras/120441ee6da5cf6b3fa98dc2897a7c16.poster.avif?t=1726635915\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201430/extras/120441ee6da5cf6b3fa98dc2897a7c16.webm?t=1726635915\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201430/extras/120441ee6da5cf6b3fa98dc2897a7c16.mp4?t=1726635915\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>With the help of the overzealous Forest Ranger Elise, and her aloof sister Frankie, Tara seeks to understand the truth behind the unusual <strong><i>Geists</i></strong>.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201430/extras/f30f0008bc423ee681c9855ba7850d41.avif?t=1726635915\" width=800 height=450 /></span>",
